  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then subsequently, I passed by [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and I saw [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] her pajamas.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] And you know, you, you lost awareness of [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] yourself or anyone else or anything, because you were on a, on a conveyor belt.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were constantly-- your, your circumstances were constantly changing violently.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, here you were, you just passed Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Mengele, and you were already marching forward.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and, and incidentally, he-- I don't exactly now know at what hour we arrived, but by the time I got to where we were eventually put into the showers, after the fashion, it was that night.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Believe me, I didn't notice that time has gone by and, and it went from day to night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Time had all flown together, flowed together, and, and, and became one unrecognizable and undistinguishable and inseparable process, a kind of a, a, a flow [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] without knowing certainly any difference between one hour and, and one day or one month or one year.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was an incredibly well-organized and efficient procedure that was elementary, and perhaps, because of that, so effective.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And everything about it was elementary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I passed through Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mengele.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In front of me was the youngest brother of a lifelong friend of mine who lives in the United States.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I do not know to this day-- and this is, again, part of the same problem, in a way, of the time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, Mengele was going like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I don't know whether or not he didn't point him to go to the life side and me to the wrong side.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
